  "3309160": {
    "name": "Chronocracy",
    "steam_appid": 3309160,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Chronocracy》</strong>是一款刺激的即时战略游戏。你将领导一个小型文明，发展社会，在奇异的平面世界上顽强生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领你的部落，明智地调配力量与资源，抵御周边部落的侵袭，揭开隐匿于时间长河中的秘密，让文明远离毁灭的厄运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/2f553e79338781270daf08fb8c49cb4a.poster.avif?t=1768387226\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/2f553e79338781270daf08fb8c49cb4a.webm?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/2f553e79338781270daf08fb8c49cb4a.mp4?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索地表与地下深处，建造矿井，收集珍稀资源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发展城市，掌控星球。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用从传统农业到前沿先进科学的各类技术。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探寻有效管理资源与定居点的新工具。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建强大的军队，从弓箭手和长矛手小队，到直升机和巨型泰坦，应有尽有！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他文明结成外交联盟。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越时空，改写部落的命运。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将《Chronocracy》加入愿望清单，订阅最新消息，深入了解这个有待统治的世界！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/a8f9a5190b5af25bcd79ed5c1e39ff97.avif?t=1768387226\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras_big/a8f9a5190b5af25bcd79ed5c1e39ff97.avif?t=1768387226 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领三个部落之一，通过建立繁荣的城市网络并探索整个星球，将你的部落带向辉煌！以一座市政厅和少数忠诚的追随者起步，缔造高度发达的文明，使其不仅能直面毛茸茸的胖鸟，还能应对可怕的入侵者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/c4681a29ec69069a33c2f77d1cf8a353.poster.avif?t=1768387226\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/c4681a29ec69069a33c2f77d1cf8a353.webm?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/c4681a29ec69069a33c2f77d1cf8a353.mp4?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聘请学者，研究科技，解锁新技术与建筑。超过15座独特建筑等你来探索，每一座都能让文明向星球霸主地位更进一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发展基础设施：建造房屋，确保食物与资源生产。建造经济建筑，用于贸易、开采珍稀材料以及生产独特资源。建造强大的军事建筑保卫领土，用弓箭、长矛和枪炮武装人民，甚至可以生产胖鸟骑兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/7b3f2f97bb95f8a4d577f663fb96a445.avif?t=1768387226\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras_big/7b3f2f97bb95f8a4d577f663fb96a445.avif?t=1768387226 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Chronocracy》的平面世界看似宁静舒适，但其迷人外表下隐藏着可能摧毁文明的致命威胁。你将遭遇形形色色的敌人，从胖鸟和幼虫等狡黠的当地生物，到心怀不轨的敌对邻邦，再到来自遥远之地的神秘黑暗访客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/46a93150e9641588eb218423fc680d20.poster.avif?t=1768387226\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/46a93150e9641588eb218423fc680d20.webm?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/46a93150e9641588eb218423fc680d20.mp4?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了生存下去，你需要高效地采集与生产资源，保持战斗单位和生产单位之间的平衡，揭开神秘敌人的秘密，并趁敌人尚未壮大将其消除。你能保护好你的文明，并将其发展成足以征服这个奇异世界的强大力量吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/c35ced2ac9a960cf68718603d702859a.avif?t=1768387226\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras_big/c35ced2ac9a960cf68718603d702859a.avif?t=1768387226 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源采集与生产是文明赖以生存与发展的关键。这里有20多种不同类型的资源，能满足繁荣发展所需的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/a32907fe5f31f40dbf8c69884e6f3645.poster.avif?t=1768387226\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/a32907fe5f31f40dbf8c69884e6f3645.webm?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/a32907fe5f31f40dbf8c69884e6f3645.mp4?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些资源需要在地表或地下深处开采，而其他资源只能通过科学进步与先进技术来创造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/26f9869eab4f93a754694499c6171db9.poster.avif?t=1768387226\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/26f9869eab4f93a754694499c6171db9.webm?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309160/extras/26f9869eab4f93a754694499c6171db9.mp4?t=1768387226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等你掌握了时间管理技术，就能获取一种独特资源——超材料，它是制造强大泰坦以及抵御可怕入侵者的基础。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为资源管理大师，借此将文明打造成一支无敌之师。向着丰功伟绩前进！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 俄语, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 捷克语, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 繁体中文, 土耳其语",
